org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.filesystem.compat

Class PathDataImageJAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.filesystem.compat.PathDataImageJAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImageJDatatypeAdapter

    public class PathDataImageJAdapter
extends Object
implements ImageJDatatypeAdapter
    Allows importing of path data from within ImageJ The main 'ImageJ' data type is File, but this also allows conversion from String, Path and ResultsTable.
